{"title":"2020-07-02","virtualPath":"/Diary/","html":"<p>CATAN そろそろか</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://game.watch.impress.co.jp/docs/news/1262724.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Niantic、スマートフォン向け新作アプリ「CATAN」のβ版提供をもうすぐスタート</a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>あめ足りなくて最大強化まであと 150 アメほど。ライコウを越え、すでに電気系最強 <g-emoji class=\"g-emoji\" alias=\"grin\" fallback-src=\"https://github.githubassets.com/images/icons/emoji/unicode/1f601.png\">😁</g-emoji></p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-07-02/20200701-223832-Screenshot_20200701-223832.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-07-02/20200701-223832-Screenshot_20200701-223832.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>まじでうれしい。</p>\n","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"日記","updated":"2020-07-03T15:32:40","published":"2020-07-03T15:32:40"}